headline.main: ENGLAND.; POLITICAL INTELLIGENCE. General Aspect of the Eastern Question. Literary and Theatrical Intelligence.

docs.lead_paragraph: Since the commencement of hostilities on the Danube, every day has brought an installment of news, mole or less important, and let it be added, more or less contradictory. For the details, I refer you to the various accounts given in the papers, leaving you to decide as to what seems to be most trustworthy. Corrected bulletins have yet to arrive,
